receiving a retained rate of basic pay under section 5363, the rate of basic pay payable under such section; and”.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1993—Par. (8). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/89/s3/b/1/E/i"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–89, § 3(b)(1)(E)(i)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subpar. (C) as (B) and struck out former subpar. (B) which read as follows: “in the case of an employee covered by the performance management and recognition system, the rates of basic pay under chapter 54; and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (9). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/89/s3/b/1/E/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–89, § 3(b)(1)(E)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “applies” for “applies (including any position under the performance management and recognition system)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1992—Par. (1)(C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/378/s2/25/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–378, § 2(25)(A)","children":[],"tail":", amended subpar. (C) generally. Prior to amendment, subpar. (C) read as follows: “chapter 73 of title 38, relating to the Veterans Health Services and Research Administration;”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (8)(C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/378/s2/25/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–378, § 2(25)(B)","children":[],"tail":", added subpar. (C)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idb8387e5d-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idb8387e5e-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2004 Amendmen